author: pburba
msg: Code and documentation improvements to some merge.c helper functions.
(filter_merged_revisions): Improve doc string and comments.  Remove
requested_merge and is_rollback and replace with two revision args.  This
makes it clear that the requested rangelist is always just one range.
(calculate_remaining_ranges): Move some setup code needed only by
filter_merged_revisions into the latter.  Get rid of unnecessary
inheritable arg.  Update call to filter_merged_revisions().
